image_analysis.description: A photograph of a home gym or fitness room. The room has light-colored wood flooring and textured tan/beige wallpaper. Four pieces of exercise equipment are visible against the back wall: a white Cybex back extension machine, a silver/grey weight bench or Roman chair, a black stationary spin bike, and a black recumbent exercise bike. A white sign with the letter 'Z' is taped to the wall above the spin bike. A white door frame is visible on the right side of the image.
